message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero
